{"abstract":[{"text":"This session will help you take advantage of the Multi-Touch features available in iOS. You will learn practical information about Multi-Touch APIs, touch routing, gesture recognizers, as well as guidelines for interoperating with the system and other apps, and pointers for how to create complex real-world user interfaces which make great use of Multi-Touch.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/118\/","type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","isActive":true}},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-118-Making-the-Most-of-MultiTouch-on-iOS","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-118-making-the-most-of-multitouch-on-ios"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC11","role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Making the Most of Multi-Touch on iOS"},"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC11":{"role":"collectionGroup","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDC11-Icon.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"WWDC11.jpeg"}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes